serviceDesc: Cleanings prevent tooth decay and tooth loss. Cal Select Dental Group in San Bernardino, Hesperia, and Riverside California, offers in-depth cleanings for children and adults. Your customized teeth cleaning gets rid of stubborn plaque and tartar. During a cleaning, Han Kim, DDS, and the team also examine your teeth and gums. They check for dental problems that could put your oral health at risk.
